            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "FORCE",
      "description": "Force to auxiliary storage",
      "help": "Force to auxiliary storage (FORCE)\n\nSpecifies whether the data queue is forced to auxiliary storage when entries are sent or received for this data queue.\n\nNote: This parameter is valid only when TYPE(*STD) is specified.",
